<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l20"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc Alſo ıſt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> daʒ du vns gen <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_152_r1l22"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem künig darinn <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ſeinen 
